        <p>Preparing for Christopher Nolan's <em>The Odyssey</em> releasing July 17, 2026? <a href="/before-the-nolan-film">Start here →</a></p>
        <p>Or explore <a href="/gift-guide">gift ideas for classics readers</a> — beautiful editions, collector's sets, and reading tools.</p>
